title: Nikon Capture NX2 v2.4.7+Serial
description:
Capture NX2 is a photo editing and enhancements tool that allows you to edit a variety of images from standard definition to high definition. Nikon Capture NX2 allows you to analyze the elements of color, saturation and brightness, image sharpening, as well as recognize similar areas where the edit will be applied. Capture NX 2 is equipped with the latest technology to edit and enhance the photos quality more natural look.

Nikon Capture NX2 Key Features:

Adjust camera-made settings
Auto Color Aberration
Auto Retouch Brush
Batch Processing
Black and White Control
Color Management
Image Transformation
Noise Reduction
Selection Control
Shadow Adjustments, and many more.


Requirements:

Windows XP/Vista/7/8/8.1/10 (32-bit/64-bit)
1024 x 768 display
1 GB RAM
200 MB disk space


How to install?:

Disconnect from internet
Complete Capture NX 2 Installation
Run and register with serial
Block the program by a firewall (Must)
